Description: TMJOs system identity (/etc/os-release, lsb-release, issue)
 Replaces the Ubuntu identity files with TMJOs-branded versions:
  * /etc/os-release    — TMJOs 1.x (insano), shows in GNOME About
                         and modern tools that read PRETTY_NAME / ID
  * /etc/lsb-release   — KEPT AS UBUNTU NOBLE intentionally so that
