  * /etc/issue.net     — same content for telnet/ssh banner
 .
 Implementation: uses dpkg-divert to take ownership of the four
 files from the upstream base-files package. Originals are renamed
 with .tmjos-orig suffix and restored cleanly on package removal.
 base-files is "essential" so we can't Conflicts/Replaces it; divert
 is the policy-friendly way.

